text: Li Chunjian (; ; born 3 April 1996) is a Chinese bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of China Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
